20our%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20from%20both%20our%20peer%20network%20and%20within%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20husband%20was%20never%20that%20interested%20in%20kids%20until%20we%20had%20our%20own%2C%20he%20has%20since%20blossomed%20as%20a%20dad%2C%20insisting%20that%20he%20thrives%20even%20with%20little%20downtime%20as%20he%20enjoys%20spending%20time%20with%20our%20two%20boys%20so%20much.%20Certainly%2C%20there's%20no%20better%20sound%20than%20hearing%20their%20eruptions%20of%20laughter%20at%20yet%20another%20of%20dad's%20silly%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20that%20when%20my%20husband%20ended%20up%20feeling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-when-you-hate-work-job-microsoft-hr-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunfulfilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20last%20full-time%20role%2C%20it%20didn't%20take%20him%20long%20to%20decide%20that%20he%20would%20feel%20more%20satisfied%20taking%20care%20of%20our%20kids.%20This%20opened%20up%20the%20space%20for%20me%20to%20open%20myself%20up%20to%20full%E2%80%94time%20work%20as%20a%20freelance%20journalist%2C%20from%20my%20previous%20part-time%20capacity%2C%20and%20for%20us%20both%20to%20lean%20into%20the%20environment%20where%20we're%20most%20happy.%20While%20we're%20now%20settled%20into%20our%20roles%2C%20there%20are%20some%20things%20that%20have%20really%20surprised%20me%20about%20our%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226745aee5-df45-458d-bf12-5c58fcd61102%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20knows%20things%20about%20our%20kids%20that%20I%20don't%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20revelations%20for%20me%20is%20that%20my%20husband%20has%20come%20to%20know%20certain%20things%20about%20our%20kids%20more%20intimately%20than%20I%20do.%20For%20example%2C%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-went-from-having-three-picky-eaters-to-none-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20preferences%3C%2Fa%3