22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsole-breadwinner-single-income-family-budget-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20stay%20at%20home%20moms%20in%20our%20school%20peer%20group%20and%20nobody%20asks%20them%20the%20same%20thing.%20Likewise%2C%20no%20one%20asks%20when%20the%20stay%20at%20home%20moms%20plan%20to%20get%20a%20job%2C%20but%20I%20regularly%20get%20asked%20this%20about%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20situation%20might%20not%20be%20permanent%2C%20as%20we're%20happy%20to%20flex%20as%20different%20opportunities%20arise%2C%20but%20I%20can%20bet%20that%20if%20I%20returned%20to%20being%20the%20primary%20carer%2C%20fewer%20people%20would%20ask%20about%20my%20career%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlder%20people%20also%20seem%20to%20assume%20that%20my%20husband%20is%20working%20and%20I%20am%20at%20home%20with%20the%20kids.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20a%20recent%20family%20gathering%20an%20old%20family%20friend%20was%20with%20us%20looking%20on%20as%20our%20boys%20ran%20around%20the%20room.%20We%20were%20talking%20about%20what%20a%20handful%20they%20are%2C%20and%20the%20friend%20said%20to%20my%20husband%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20your%20wife%20does%20all%20the%20work%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20friend%20also%20asked%20whether%20I%20was%20a%20terrible%20cook%2C%20because%20my%20husband%20looked%20like%20he'd%20lost%20weigh.%20Little%20did%20they%20know%2C%20he%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwife-housework-until-husband-split-chores-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecook%20in%20our%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20always%20has%20been%2C%20even%20before%20we%20had%20kids.%20These%20kinds%20of%20preconceptions%20from%20older%20generations%20are%20unhelpful%2C%20but%20I%20try%20not%20to%20take%20it%20too%20personally%20and%20remember%20that%20things%20used%20to%20be%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c2cf0ba-bc