ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fopub%2Fmlr%2F1995%2F08%2Fart6full.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E95%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20all%20clothing%20bought%20by%20Americans%20was%20made%20in%20America.%20Now%20it's%20less%20than%205%25%20so%20the%20bottom%20is%20falling%20out%20of%20that%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20left%20is%20a%20very%20kind%20of%20disaggregated%20supply%20chain%2C%20meaning%20you'll%20have%20a%20yarning%20operation%20here%2C%20a%20dying%20and%20finishing%20operation%20there%2C%20a%20knitting%20operation%20there.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20have%20production%20domestically%2C%20you%20have%20to%20support%20all%20of%20that%20separated%20and%20atomized%20production%2C%20and%20that%20just%20makes%20it%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20China%2C%20you%20can%20go%20and%20say%20you%20need%20100%2C000%20purple%20T%20shirts%20with%20frills%20on%20the%20sleeves%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%2020%20factories%20bidding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20really%20get%20into%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20assemble%20it%20ourselves%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20and%20hold%20it%20together.%20It's%20gotten%20a%20lot%20easier%20now%20because%20our%20volumes%20have%20grown%20and%20now%20we're%20not%20the%20only%20people%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20harder%20and%20it's%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20quality%20is%20a%20lot%20higher%20because%20you%20can%20just%20get%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20the%20source.%20It's%20definitely%20not%20the%20easy%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c77ffa32-5098-4a87-8263-df2a7a1d1c6b%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20misunderstanding%20about%20what's%20possible%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bins%20of%20apparel%20at%20an%20American%20Giant%20facility.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802728ea466d2b74ab391c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20American%20Gia