%20businesses%20big%20and%20small%2C%20it%20is%20very%20destabilizing.%20When%20private%20sector%20businesses%20feel%20like%20things%20are%20unpredictable%20or%20unstable%2C%20that%20freezes%20capital%20and%20people%20stop%20moving%20%E2%80%94%20and%20stop%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20going%20to%20be%20supply%20chain%20ramifications%20for%20the%20current%20approach%2C%20and%20so%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20it%20plays%20out%20is%20going%20to%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20many%2C%20many%20things%20that%20we%20rely%20on%20China%20completely%20for%2C%20like%20pipe%20fittings%2C%20that%20we%20take%20for%20granted%20and%20make%20the%20economy%20work.%20What%20happens%20if%20those%20become%20two%20or%20three%20times%20more%20expensive%20to%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20businesses%20that%20supply%20our%20plumbers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20like%20the%20instability.%20I%20don't%20like%20the%20threat%20of%20the%20speed%20and%20the%20breadth%20of%20this%20stuff.%20And%20I%20certainly%20don't%20think%20that%20we%20ought%20to%20be%20treating%2C%20you%20know%2C%20our%20friendly%20allies%2C%20like%2C%20let's%20say%20Canada%20and%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20same%20way%20we're%20treating%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20very%2C%20very%20different%20situations%2C%20and%20ought%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bff6dca5-59bd-4a57-b470-b3852a20a30e%5C%22%3EThe%20United%20States%20was%20the%20knitwear%20capital%20of%20the%20world%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harvesting%20cotton%20for%20American%20Giant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680272d0c6ad288d147e8ef5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican%20Giant%20sources%20its%20cotton%20from%20US%20farms.%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Giant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20still%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20cotton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20primary%20yarn%20supplier%20is%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20yarn.%20There%20is%20plenty%20of%20cotton%20and%20yarn%20to%20handle%20whatever%20business%20we%20could%20throw%20at%20the%20US%20supply%20chain.%20Dying%20and%20finishing%20capacity%20would%20be%20fine.%20It's%20really%20at%20the%20very%20end%20%E2%80%94%20the%20sewing%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20manual%20step%20in%20the%20process%20%E2%80%94%20that%20would%20take%20some%20time%20to%20spin%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20have%20a%20T-shirt%20program%20at%20Walmart%20that%20is%20very%20large%20volume%2C%20and%20we've%20had%20no%20problem%20meeting%20that%20demand%2C%20and%20it%20could%20quadruple%20overnight%20fairly%20easily.%20And%20that's%20just%20little%20old%20American%20Giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20there's%20plenty%20of%20knit%20capacity%20here%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20cotton%20and%20yarn%20capacity%20to%20handle%20any%20kind%20of%20increase%20in%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20textile%20machinery%20is%20coming%20from%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20Germany%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Italy%2C%20which%20raises%20an%20interesting%20question%3A%20Why%20is%20it%20coming%20to%20the%20United%20States%20versus%20being%20made%20here%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skills%20gap%20question%20is%20also%20a%20really%20interesting%20one.%20We%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-masculine-many-manufacturing-jobs-factories-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20have%20people%20who%20want%20to%20fill%20some%20of%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20convince%20people%20to%20come%20over%20here%20instead%20of%20working%20at%20a%20fast-food%20restaurant%3F%20We'll%20train%20you%20to%20seamstress%2C%20we'll%20give%20you%2040%20or%2050%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20you%20could%20learn%20a%20lot%2C%20you%20can%20grow.%20I%20think%20that%20will%20happen%2C%20it%20just%20will%20take%20a%20bit%20of%20