g%20to%20revert%20back%20to%20a%20place%20where%20everything%20that%20we%20consume%20is%20made%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20between%20there%20and%20where%20we%20are%20now%2C%20there%20is%20a%20more%20rational%20middle%20ground%20that%20I%20think%20will%20reinject%20some%20vitality%20back%20into%20these%20communities%20that%20need%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-giant-ceo-us-trade-needs-reset-manufacturing-comeback-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745229602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68027331a466d2b74ab391f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-giant-ceo-us-trade-needs-reset-manufacturing-comeback-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayard%20Winthrop%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20California-based%20American%20Giant%2C%20says%20US%20manufacturing%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20it%20currently%20does.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-giant-ceo-us-trade-needs-reset-manufacturing-comeback-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yemen's%20Huthis%20say%20US%20strikes%20on%20Sanaa%20kill%20at%20least%2012%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745229569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120483144%2Cimgsize-1395550.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-huthis-say-us-strikes-on-sanaa-kill-at-least-12%2Farticleshow%2F120483004.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F120483004.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EYemen's%2