nk%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineering%2C%20are%20now%20mired%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20uncertainty%20as%20AI%20increasingly%20becomes%20capable%20of%20various%20coding%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20welcomed%20job%20transitions%20long%20before%20the%20AI%20revolution%20took%20off%2C%20and%20she's%20learned%20a%20few%20things.%20This%20is%20her%20advice%20for%20navigating%20career%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22239f931c-10ed-4f7f-876e-3ea1c79114c1%5C%22%3ELean%20into%20your%20network%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20recommends%20leveraging%20your%20network%20if%20you're%20thinking%20about%20making%20a%20career%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20entail%20talking%20to%20friends%20or%20former%20coworkers%20outside%20your%20company%20to%20find%20out%20more%20about%20what%20they%20do.%20Or%2C%20you%20can%20channel%20your%20existing%20colleagues%20and%20see%20if%20there's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20a%20switch%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20advantage%20of%20the%20network%20that%20you%20have%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Centoni%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20can%20connect%20you%20with%20different%20things%2C%20open%20up%20opportunities%2C%20mentors%2C%20sponsors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20said%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20see%20beyond%20the%20work%20you%20do%20and%20the%20world%20you%20live%20in.%20Speaking%20to%20others%20can%20help%20you%20see%20it%20%26quot%3Bmore%20broadly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ce5d9cd-5ae1-4d0a-8e18-b05e6a0efb6d%5C%22%3EWiden%20your%20search%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20said%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20flexible%2C%20curious%2C%20and%20open-minded%20gave%20her%20access%20to%20more%20opportunities%20and%20eventually%20led%20her%20down%20the%20path%20of%20executive%20leadership.%20While%20it%20may%20be%20simpler%20to%20follow%20a%20linear%20path%2C%20Centoni%20suggests%20broadening%20your%20search%20and%20looking%20for%20opportunities%20that%20create%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20about%20areas%20where%20you've%20got%20to%20look%20broadly%20versus%20what%20you're%20doing%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Centoni%20said.%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20an%20opportunity%20for%20you%20to%20kind%20of%20redefine%20the%20future%2C%20versus%20just%20working%20through%20what%20somebody's%20already%20defined%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20said%20she%20likes%20to%20pursue%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20that's%20not%20perfect%2C%20but%20has%20potential.%26quot%3B%20Sometimes%20those%20opportunities%20appear%20less%20clear%20or%20structured%2C%20she%20said.%20For%20Centoni%2C%20they've%20come%20with%20learning%20new%20technologies%20and%20domains%2C%20which%20wasn't%20always%20effortless.%20However%2C%20they%20allowed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20opportunity%20to%20create%20something%26quot%3B%20and%20felt%20more%20rewarding%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20left%20a%20footprint%20on%20all%20of%20these%20organizations%2C%20because%20the%20bold%20thinking%2C%20the%20disruptions%2C%26quot%3B%20Centoni%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20part%20that%20makes%20her%20the%20proudest%20is%20that%20the%20teams%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20thrive%26quot%3B%20after%20she%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baa36322-39ff-4907-b2ab-2b65438cf38e%5C%22%3EBrace%20for%20discomfort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Centoni's%20success%20in%20stepping%20into%20new%20roles%2C%20the%20Cisco%20executive%20has%20also%20struggled%20to%20make%20those%20transitions%20and%20find%20peace%20with%20them%20in%20the%20months%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20competing%20kind%20of%20voices%20in%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Centoni%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20that%20wants%20to%20learn%20new%20things%20every%20single%20time%2C%20which%20means%20you're%20starting%20with%20something%20new.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20also%20want%20to%20be%20really%20confident%20in%20the%20work%20that%20I%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentoni%20said%20one%20of%20her%20b