2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-has-50-direct-reports-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%20directly%20to%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20sets%20the%20direction%20and%20the%20goal%2C%20but%20the%20Santa%20Clara%2C%20California-based%20company%20also%20has%20a%20defining%20mantra%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20mission%20is%20the%20boss%2C%26quot%3B%20author%20Tae%20Kim%20wrote%20in%20his%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%20Nvidia%20Way%3A%20Jensen%20Huang%20and%20the%20Making%20of%20a%20Tech%20Giant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20shies%20away%20from%20short-term%20goals%2C%20Kim%20said%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThere%20is%20a%20central%20goal%20or%20mission%2C%20but%20planning%20and%20strategizing%20are%20constant%20processes%20that%20don't%20focus%20on%20management%20incentives%20or%20satisfying%20a%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20leaders%20may%20suddenly%20find%20themselves%20reporting%20directly%20to%20Huang.%20These%20newly%20anointed%20direct%20reports%20are%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bpilots%20in%20charge%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20subject%20to%20his%20wrath%20and%20carry%20his%20weight%2C%20Kim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20former%20Nvidia%20employee%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20discuss%20internal%20matters%2C%20everyone%20in%20the%20company%20must%20be%20prepared%20to%20answer%20Huang%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20ability%20to%20track%20small%20details%20across%20countless%20projects%20is%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20director%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20of%20extreme%20accountability%20means%20Nvidia%20hasn't%20had%20to%20rein%20in%20employees%20as%20many%20other%20companies%20have%20post-pandemic.%20Nvidia%20is%20still%20remote-friendly%2C%20for%20example.%20But%20meetings%20are%20far%20from%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20is%20known%20to%20publicly%20discuss%20failures%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-leadership-style-insiders-tough-boss-admit-mistakes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisagreements%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20benefit%20the%20group%20rather%20than%20spare%20feelings.%20If%20he%20suspects%20someone%20isn't%20on%20top%20of%20their%20work%2C%20a%20public%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-leadership-style-insiders-tough-boss-admit-mistakes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecross-examination%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20ensue.%20Perks%20are%20few%2C%20but%20that's%20always%20been%20the%20case%2C%20two%20former%20Nvidians%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmission%20is%20boss%26quot%3B%20ethos%20helps%20Nvidia%20avoid%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20large%20firms%2C%20which%20often%20struggle%20to%20make%20quick%20decisions%2C%20let%20alone%20pivot%20when%20needed%2C%20Kim%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJensen%20really%20doesn't%20tolerate%20bullshit%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20engineer%20from%20Nvidia's%20early%20days%20told%20BI.%20This%20intolerance%20makes%20playing%20politics%20nearly%20impossible%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%2C%20'You%20did%20something%20wrong.'%20It's%2C%20'You%20did%20something%20wrong%20that%20was%20self-serving'%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20typical%20problem%20in%20big%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20philosophy%20is%20that%20the%20mission%20can%20change%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20everyone%20serves%20it%20rather%20than%20their%20manager%2C%20the%20company%20should%20thrive.%20Nvidia's%20pivot%20to%20focus%20on%20machine%20learning%20was%20even%20communicated%20in%20a%20companywide%20Friday-night%20email%20in%202014.%20By%20Monday%2C%20Nvidia%20was%20an%20AI%20company%2C%20Witt%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf5fbd65-faed-416d-a6ae-beb10f5d45c5%5C%22%3EEmail%20accountability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20is%20known%20to%20send%20more%20than%20100%20emails%20a%20day