atholic%20Church%20at%20the%20election%20conclave%20in%202005%20at%20the%20Vatican%2C%20Vatican%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bb55f1c040bd1b4ca2e6ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECardinals%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20at%20the%20papal%20conclave%20in%202005.%3Cp%3EArturo%20Mari%20-%20Vatican%20Pool%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20some%20papal%20conclaves%20have%20gone%20on%20for%20weeks%2C%20months%2C%20even%20years.%20Notably%2C%20the%20conclave%20of%201268%20lasted%20over%20two%20years%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-longest-papal-conclave-ever-2013-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecardinals%20were%20eventually%20given%20only%20water%20and%20bread%20to%20try%20to%20force%20them%20into%20a%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConclaves%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20relatively%20short.%20The%20one%20in%202013%20took%20just%20two%20days.%20The%20longest%20papal%20conclave%20in%20the%2020th%20century%20was%20in%201922%2C%20when%20the%20cardinals%20voted%2014%20times%20over%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20conclave%20lasts%20more%20than%2012%20or%2013%20days%2C%20the%20cardinals%20can%20swap%20over%20to%20majority%20voting%20to%20expedite%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224875dc82-ac66-43bd-93c2-2e4f67a91d7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20new%20pope%20will%20be%20named%20after%20white%20smoke%20is%20seen%20from%20the%20chimney%20of%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20smoke%20seen%20rising%20from%20the%20chimney%20on%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel%20mean%20a%20new%20pontiff%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20selected.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bb56784e7cbbbe3dc44921%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlack%20smoke%20rising%20from%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel%20means%20a%20new%20pontiff%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20selected.%3Cp%3EJohannes%20Eisele%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20candidate%20has%20been%20selected%2C%20it%20is%20up%20to%20them%20to%20accept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BAccepto%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20accept%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20papal%20conclave%20is%20over%2C%20and%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20has%20found%20its%20new%20pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outside%20world%20will%20know%20that%20a%20new%20pope%20has%20been%20elected%20once%20white%20smoke%20is%20seen%20coming%20from%20the%20chimney%20above%20the%20Sistine%20Chapel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmoke%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20onlookers%20twice%20a%20day%20throughout%20the%20conclave%20process%2C%20but%2C%20crucially%2C%20it%20will%20appear%20white%20only%20if%20the%20next%20pontiff%20has%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20scrutineers%20douse%20the%20discarded%20ballots%20with%20mystery%20chemicals%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2013%2F03%2F12%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frecipe-for-conclaves-black-and-white-smoke-remains-mystery.html%3Fref%3Dworld%26_r%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eor%20something%20else%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20clear)%20to%20make%20the%20smoke%20black%20if%20there%20isn't%20a%20pope%2C%20and%20make%20the%20smoke%20white%20in%20the%20event%20that%20%26quot%3BHabemus%20papam%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20translates%20as%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20pope%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20is%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224890%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Newly%20elected%20Pope%20Francis%20I%20waves%20to%20the%20waiting%20crowd%20from%20the%20central%20balcony%20of%20St%20Peter's%20Basilica%20on%20March%2013%2C%202013%20in%20Vatican%20City%2C%20Vatican.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http