%20that%20underpins%20bets.%20It's%20also%20working%20on%20other%20ways%20to%20engage%20fans%20of%20niche%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EALT%20Sports%20Data%20competes%20with%20big%20sports%20data%20providers%20like%20Sportradar%20and%20Genius%20Sports%2C%20which%20work%20with%20major%20leagues%20such%20as%20the%20NBA%20and%20NFL.%20The%20startup%20aims%20to%20set%20itself%20apart%20by%20prioritizing%20niche%20and%20lifestyle%20sports%20that%20its%20competitors%20aren't%20focusing%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20leagues%20out%20there%20that%20are%20not%20the%20NFL%2C%20the%20MLB%2C%20the%20NBA%2C%20that%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20I%20feel%20have%20been%20systemically%20set%20up%20for%20failure%20in%20sports%20betting%20because%20there's%20just%20no%20real%20innovation%20or%20thought%20put%20into%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ballard%2C%20ALT%20Sports%20Data's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EALT%20Sports%20Data%20works%20with%20sports%20such%20as%20Formula%201%2C%20which%20recently%20made%20the%20company%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altsportsdata.com%2Fpost%2Fformula-1-appoints-alt-sports-data-as-official-betting-data-supplier-to-drive-growth-in-sports-betti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20betting%20supplier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20X%20Games%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Surf%20League.%20Sportsbooks%20like%20FanDuel%20and%20DraftKings%20use%20ALT%20Sports%20Data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBallard%20said%20these%20lifestyle%20sports%20have%20massive%20fan%20bases%2C%20but%20not%20much%20representation%20on%20sportsbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20we%20bet%20on%20a%20bunch%20of%20these%20sports%20like%20surfing%20and%20motocross%3F%26quot%3B%20Ballard%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20plans%20to%20use%20its%20fresh%20funding%20to%20create%20more%20tools%20and%20partnerships%20to%20help%20make%20sports%20more%20engaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEberg%20Capital%20and%20Relay%20Ventures%20co-led%20ALT%20Sports%20Data's%20seed%20round%2C%20including%20participation%20from%20Motley%20Fool%20Ventures%2C%20Scrum%20Ventures%2C%20and%20other%20individual%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aca76ca8-51f1-450b-8bbb-cf8fda4b9c01%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EALT%20Sports%20Data's%20strategy%20to%20drive%20sports%20fan%20engagement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBallard%20said%20ALT%20Sports%20Data%20has%20four%20pillars%20of%20its%20business%20that%20help%20drive%20sports%20betting%20and%20fan%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20league%20services%20include%20data%20rights%20deals%2C%20marketing%2C%20integrity%2C%20and%20other%20work%20with%20sports%20rights%20owners.%20Ballard%20said%20the%20company%20has%20about%2025%20sports%20and%20leagues%20in%20its%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20combat%2C%20motor%2C%20action%2C%20and%20niche%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product%20arm%20supports%20those%20league%20relationships%20with%20data%20science%2C%20distribution%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20game%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20are%20we%20driving%20more%20meaningful%20relationships%20with%20leagues%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Ballard.%20He%20said%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20company%20will%20build%20the%20back-end%20data%20infrastructure%20for%20a%20league%20to%20support%20betting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20has%20a%20media%20division%20with%20its%20own%20affiliate%20site%2C%20NXTbets.%20The%20site%20uses%20content%20to%20direct%20people%20to%20sports%20betting%20platforms%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20companies%20like%20Catena%20Media%20and%20Better%20Collective%20do.%20Ballard%20said%20NXTbets%20has%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20substantial%26quot%3B%20piece%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20working%20on%20creating%20its%20own%20games%20to%20expand%20from%20sports%20betting%20into%20areas%20like%20social%2C%20peer-to-peer%2C%20daily%20fantasy%2C%20and%20free-to-play%20gam