eng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20craving%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-brand-of-frozen-pizza-from-grocery-store-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrozen%20pizza%3C%2Fa%3E%20lately%3F%20You're%20not%20alone.%20Maybe%20it's%20because%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-chipotle-burrito-season-hiring-jobs-food-eating-out-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweather's%20warmer%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20maybe%20you're%20jonesing%20for%20a%20lazy-day%20treat%2C%20or%20maybe%20it's%20because%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-recession-tariffs-goldman-sachs-stock-correction-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20market's%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-stocks-economy-world-order-deutsche-bank-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20throwing%20everything%20into%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20economy%20has%20people%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweird-recession-indicators%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession%20indicators%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20potential%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Flabor-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20market%20weakness%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-retailer-big-box-stocks-selloff-consumer-spending-strength-recession-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20pullbacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20more%20specific%20signals%20that%20suggest%20dark%20times%20are%20nigh.%20Consumers%20on%20edge%2C%20for%20example%2C%20buy%20more%20lipstick%20as%20a%20still-affordable%20luxury%2C%20or%20they%20start%20to%20scoop%20up%20smaller%20bottles%20of%20liquor.%20Another%20peculiar%20sign%20they're%20feeling%20pinched%20by%20the%20economy%3A%20They%20buy%20more%20frozen%20pizza%2C%20specifically%2C%20the%20fancy%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20happens%20every%20sort%20of%20downturn%20in%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20increased%20demand%20for%20premium%20frozen%20pizzas%2C%20high-priced%20frozen%20pizzas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Craig%20Zawada%2C%20the%20chief%20visionary%20officer%20at%20Pros%20Holdings%2C%20a%20price%20optimization%20company.%20It's%20a%20bit%20counterintuitive%2C%20he%20added%2C%20since%20you'd%20think%20consumers%20are%20more%20cost-conscious%2C%20but%20it's%20actually%20a%20trade%20that%20makes%20sense%20because%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20replacing%20eating%20out%20to%20having%20a%20good%20frozen%20pizza%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20next%20time%20you%20find%20yourself%20lingering%20in%20the%20frozen%20section%2C%20know%20that%20your%20hankering%20for%20DiGiorno%20might%20be%20due%20to%20a%20case%20of%20economic%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20are%20feeling%20pinched%20%E2%80%94%20economically%2C%20existentially%20%E2%80%94%20they%20turn%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%20frozen%20section.%20In%202009%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FSB10001424052702304739104575153682874935498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrozen%20food%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20grew%20by%203.1%25.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20frozen%20pizza%20sales%20spiked%20by%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20from%20the%20year%20before%2C%20from%20%245.8%20billion%20in%20revenue%20in%202019%20to%20%246.6%20billion%20in%20revenue%20in%202020%2C%20per%20the%20market%20research%20firm%20IBISWorld.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrozen%20pizza%20has%20always%20been%20a%20good%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20Chafetz%2C%20an%20investment%20banker%20who%20does%20dealmaking%20in%20the%20consumer%20space%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20came%20into%20focus%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20people%20weren't%20working%2C%20money%20was%20tight%2C%20and%20you%20had%20to%20feed%20a%20family%20at%20night.%20Frozen%20pizza%20is%20a%20very%20economical%20way%20to%20feed%20your%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Ryan%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Tree%20Tavern%20Pizza%2C%20a%20frozen%20pizza%20company%20that%20operates%20out%20of%20New%20Jersey%2C%20told%20me%20that%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20his%20sales%20%26quot%3Bwent%20through%20the%20roof.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20pizza%20as%20a%20category%20does%20well%20during%20downturns%2C%20but%20frozen%20has%20the%20extra%20%26quot%3Bconvenience%26quot%3B%20factor.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20ready%20to%20heat.%20No%20tipping%20the%20delivery%20person%20or%20cold%2C%20soggy%20pizza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20growth%20has%20since%20slowed%20from%20the%20breakneck%20COVID-driven%20pace%2C%20people%20are%20still%20buying%20up%20more%20frozen%20pizzas%2C%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20US%20frozen%20pizza%20industry%20generated%20%246.5%20billion%20in%20annual%20revenue%20in%202024%2C%20per%20IBISWorld%2C%20and%20remains%20well%20above%20its%20pre-pandemic%20level.%20Tighter%20budgets%20still%20make%20that%20%2410%20frozen%20pie%20seem%20pretty%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there's%20a%20growing%20amount%20of%20competition%20in%20the%20frozen%20food%20aisle%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20frozen%20pizza%20is%20still%20a%20star%20player%2C%20said%20Phil%20Lempert%2C%20a%20food%20industry%20analyst%20and%20the%20editor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsupermarketguru.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupermarketguru.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20boxes%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20and%20they're%20relatively%20attractive%20to%20display.%20They're%20also%20convenient%20for%20stores%20to%20offer%20promotions%20and%20discounts%20on%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20different%20pizza%20brands%20that%20are%20out%20there%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20every%20week%20when%20I%20look%20at%20store%20circulars%2C%20there's%20at%20least%20one%20pizza%20on%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20Lempert%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20companies%20are%20always%20vying%20to%20give%20promotions%20to%20the%20retailer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPizza%20is%20a%20comfort%20food%20that%20people%20tend%20to%20crave%20in%20trying%20times%20such%20as%20these.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20with%20everything%20that's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20country%20and%20in%20the%20world%2C%20people%20are%20very%20nervous%2C%20so%20we're%20going%20to%20gravitate%20toward%20more%20comfort%20foods%2C%20whether%20it's%20mac%20and%20cheese%2C%20whether%20it's%20hot%20dogs%2C%20whether%20it's%20pizza%2C%26quot%3B%20Lempert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMid-conversation%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20might%20be%20doing%20some%20accidental%20coping%20via%20comfort%20food%20lately%2C%20as%20I've%20made%20pizza%20(homemade%2C%20which%20was%20terrible)%20and%20mac%20and%20cheese%20(luckily%2C%20from%20the%20box)%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20are%20in%20my%20normal%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20probably%20helps%20frozen%20pizza's%20case%20that%20the%20quality%20has%20improved%20dramatically%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20varieties%20on%20offer.%20You've%20got%20healthier%20options%2C%20with%20cauliflower%20crusts%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20you%20can%20indulge%20(slightly)%20with%20premium%20ingredients%20like%20hot%20honey%2C%20prosciutto%2C%20or%20basil.%20Restaurant%20brands%20have%20launched%20their%20own%20frozen%20offerings%20so%20people%20can%20get%20something%20that%20tastes%20like%20the%20out-to-eat%20experience%20at%20home.%20Ryan%20pointed%20out%20that%20home%20freezers%20have%20also%20gotten%20bigger%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20stock%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20that%20good%20old%20economic%20anxiety%20is%20stirring%20up%20once%20again%2C%20people%20are%20leaning%20toward%20eating%20at%20home%20and%20stocking%20up%20from%20the%20grocery%20store%20frozen%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Portalatin%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20food%20industry%20advisor%20at%20Circana%2C%20a%20market%20research%20firm%2C%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20year%20or%20so%2C%20consumers%20have%20been%20opting%20to%20buy%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20their%20meals%20at%20retail%20establishments%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20grocery%20stores%2C%20clubs%2C%20online%20%E2%80%94%20than%20from%20food-service%20operations%2C%20such%20as%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20a%20reflection%20of%20several%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20response%20to%20inflation%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20food%20inflation%20away%20from%20home%20is%20still%20accelerating%20faster%20than%20at%20home.%20But%20it's%20also%20this%20sort%20of%20longer-term%20trend%20of%20a%20more%20home-centric%20consumer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20took%20hold%2C%20many%20people%20had%20to%20stay%20home.%20Once%20the%20pandemic%20subsided%2C%20they%20were%20excited%20to%20get%20back%20out%20there%20and%20go%20to%20the%20restaurants%20they%20had%20eschewed%20for%20months.%20But%20that%20stay-at-home%20muscle%20is%20still%20stronger%20than%20it%20was%20pre-pandemic.%20More%20people%20are%20working%20from%20home%2C%20where%20it's%20easy%20to%20whip%20something%20up%20in%20their%20own%20kitchens%20%E2%80%94%20Ryan%20said%20that%20while%20it%20may%20seem%20silly%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fact%20that%20many%20folks%20never%20got%20out%20of%20their%20pajamas%20helped%20spur%20sales.%26quot%3B%20Consumers%20have%20also%20grown%20more%20accustomed%20to%20having%20fun%20nights%20in%20%E2%80%94%20turns%20out%20all%20that%20practice%20in%202020%20means%20they've%20gotten%20better%20at%20at-home%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20seem%20to%20be%20more%20comfortable%20at%20home.%20They%20want%20to%20do%20their%20own%20drinking%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Chafetz%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20happy%20being%20at%20home%2C%20nesting.%20I%20think%20people%20nest%20when%20they're%20nervous%2C%20and%20so%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20going%20on%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmpirical%20evidence%20suggests%20consumers%20often%20'trade%20down'%20to%20frozen%20or%20delivered%20pizza%20during%20recessions.%20Consumers%20become%20more%20price%20sensitive%20as%20they%20opt%20for%20cheaper%2C%20family-size%20offerings%2C%20like%20pizza%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Fasciano%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20CFRA%20Research%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20He%20noted%20that%20pizza%20restaurants'%20marketing%20is%20anchored%20around%20value%2C%20too%2C%20such%20as%20Domino's%20recently%20launched%20appeal%20to%20more%20budget-conscious%20consumers%3A%20the%20%26quot%3BEmergency%20Pizza%26quot%3B%20promotion%20(a%20free%20pizza)%20and%20%26quot%3BBest%20Deal%20Ever%26quot%3B%20promotion%20(a%20%249.99%20deal).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20again%2C%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20just%20any%20old%20traded-down%20item%20people%20are%20buying%20as%20they%20start%20to%20worry%20about%20where%20the%20economy%20is%20headed%2C%20frozen%20pizza%20or%20otherwise%3B%20it's%20the%20nicer%20stuff.%20It's%20reflective%20of%20this%20overarching%20attitude%20among%20American%20consumers%20that%20we%20still%20want%20to%20treat%20ourselves%2C%20even%20as%20we%20cut%20back%20in%20other%20areas.%20Many%20people%20buckle%20down%20on%20their%20budgets%20somewhat%2C%20but%20they%20also%20spring%20for%20treats%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-prices-futures-soaring-climate-change-drought-bitter-beans-flavor-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efancy%20latte%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20weekend%20getaway%2C%20or%20a%20frozen%20pizza%20they%20tell%20themselves%20is%20healthy%2C%20which%2C%20maybe%2C%20don't%20look%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20too%20hard%20at%20the%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20we've%20seen%20the%20headwind%20at%20restaurants%20and%20the%20tailwind%20at%20making%20meals%20at%20home%20because%20they're%20more%20affordable.%20Yet%20there%20are%20all%20kinds%20of%20examples%20where%20we%20will%20choose%20the%20more%20premium%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20Portalatin%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20go%20to%20retail%2C%20we%20may%20not%20be%20choosing%20the%20lowest%20price%20point%20offering%2C%20recognizing%20that%20we're%20already%20saving%20money%20by%20cooking%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20have%20been%20battening%20down%20the%20hatches%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20Heightened%20concerns%20around%20tariffs%20have%20led%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fconsumer-sentiment-plummets-11-in-april-on-trade-war-fears-1034576461%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacute%20sense%20of%20dread%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20many%20Americans%20about%20prices%2C%20economic%20stability%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-worried-unemployment-layoffs-recession-jobs-hiring-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20own%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20the%20type%20of%20mix%20that%20might%20make%20that%20stay-at-home%20Red%20Baron%20extra%20enticing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Curtis%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20analyst%20at%20IBISWorld%2C%20said%20they're%20not%20forecasting%20an%20economic-freak-out-induced%20spike%20in%20frozen%20pizza%20sales%20like%20the%20ones%20in%202009%20or%202020%2C%20in%20part%20because%20it's%20not%20clear%20what%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20overall%20economy.%20But%20in%20the%20event%20that%20things%20really%20start%20to%20go%20south%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20logic%20of%20buying%20the%20frozen%20pizza%20when%20you%20have%20less%20money%20would%20still%20hold%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20added%20that%20frozen%20pizza%20is%20facing%20more%20competition%20for%20consumer%20dollars%20than%20it%20did%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20with%20more%20frozen%20options%20available%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20proliferation%20of%20delivery%20services%20that%20make%20it%20possible%20to%20get%20all%20kinds%20of%20foods%20dropped%20off%20right%20to%20your%20door.%20Obviously%2C%20cooking%20at%20home%20is%20still%20cheaper%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20account%20for%20all%20the%20fees%20and%20the%20tip%2C%20but%20many%20consumers%20are%20still%20doing%20some%20slight%20splurging.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20consumers%20that%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20these%20fees%20just%20for%20the%20convenience%20of%20delivery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%2C%20from%20Tree%20Tavern%2C%20said%20he's%20not%20really%20concerned%20about%20competition%20from%20delivery%20or%20restaurants%2C%20because%20he%20sees%20frozen%20as%20its%20own%20thing.%20His%20customers%20are%20loyal%2C%20and%20he's%20focused%20on%20quality%20and%20authenticity%20that%20he%20hopes%20will%20appeal%20to%20people%20in%20good%20times%20and%20bad.%20He%20only%20sells%20plain%20cheese%20pizza%2C%20which%20helps%20keep%20the%20price%20stable%20and%20gives%20customers%20the%20opportunity%20to%20dress%20the%20pizza%20up%20however%20they%20like.%20%26quot%3BI%20kid%20with%20people%20who%20ask%20me%20why%20I%20don't%20offer%20more%20toppings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20jokingly%20say%2C%20'Buy%20your%20own%20damn%20pepperoni!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20economy%20takes%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20customers%20may%20stick%20with%20just%20the%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrozen-pizza-sales-recession-indicator-stock-market-crash-consumer-trends-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745223062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a230c6ad288d147e9a3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrozen-pizza-sales-recession-indicator-stock-market-crash-consumer-trends-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20people%20get%20nervous%20about%20the%20economy%2C%20they%20turn%20to%20cheaper%20comfort%20food%20options%20like%20frozen%20pizza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrozen-pizza-sales-recession-indicator-stock-market-crash-consumer-trends-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Timeline%20of%20Sidharth%20Malhotra%20and%20Kiara%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20love%20story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745223059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120476946%2Cimgsize-93804.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffrom-falling-in-love-to-awaiting-parenthood-a-complete-timeline-of-sidharth-malhotra-and-kiara-advanis-love-story%2Fphotostory%2F120476946.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F1