p-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarth%20Tatva%20started%20its%20commercial%20operations%20in%202021%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20turning%20ceramic%20waste%20into%20something%20usable%20is%20complex%2C%20yet%20the%2032-year-old%20has%20managed%20to%20create%20a%20sustainable%20system%20that%20can%20be%20scaled.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20starts%20by%20sourcing%20post-industrial%20ceramic%20waste%20from%20factories%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20specifically%20in%20Morbi%20and%20Thangadh%2C%20where%20the%20waste%20is%20pulverised%20into%20a%20fine%20powder.%20We%20mix%2060%25%20pulverised%20ceramic%20waste%20with%2040%25%20of%20our%20specially%20designed%20clay%20binder%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mixture%20is%20processed%20using%20a%20ball%20mill%2C%20which%20helps%20blend%20everything%20thoroughly.%20For%20products%20like%20mugs%20and%20partitions%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20slip%20casting%2C%20where%20the%20liquid%20mixture%20is%20poured%20into%20moulds%20and%20allowed%20to%20solidify.%20Alternatively%2C%20when%20creating%20dough-like%20material%20for%20pottery%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20dewatered%20using%20a%20filter%20press%20and%20then%20passed%20through%20a%20pug%20mill%20to%20ensure%20uniform%20consistency.%20This%20mixture%20is%20named%20Tatva%20mix%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20desired%20consistency%20is%20achieved%2C%20Tatva%20Mix%20can%20be%20used%20by%20artists%20and%20designers%20to%20create%20various%20products%2C%20from%20food%20bowls%20to%20tiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20product%20from%20recycled%20material%20can%20be%20arduous%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20try%20it%20out%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20first%20hurdles%20we%20faced%20was%20cracking%20the%20clay%20moulds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20testing%2C%20tweaking%20the%20composition%2C%20and%20adjusti