ional%20and%20artistic%20pieces%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20he%20faced%20was%20educating%20consumers%20about%20the%20complexities%20of%20recycling%20ceramic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20ceramic%20or%20clay%20products%20are%20inherently%20eco-friendly.%20While%20it%20is%20true%20that%20ceramics%20are%20made%20from%20natural%20materials%2C%20the%20process%20of%20creating%20them%20is%20not%20energy-efficient.%20Firing%20ceramics%20at%20high%20temperatures%20requires%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20energy%2C%20which%20makes%20their%20production%20quite%20resource-intensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20large-scale%20machinery%2C%20only%20hand-made%20pieces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20is%20operating%20on%20a%20smaller%20and%20more%20sustainable%20scale.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20at%20a%20studio%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20piece%20is%20handmade%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20rely%20on%20large-scale%20machinery%20or%20an%20extensive%20workforce.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20guarantees%20that%20every%20product%20is%20carefully%20crafted%2C%20which%20not%20only%20reduces%20the%20reliance%20on%20heavy%20industrial%20processes%20but%20also%20keeps%20the%20energy%20consumption%20lower%20compared%20to%20mass-produced%20ceramics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanzariya%20Ankit%2C%20Technical%20Material%20Manager%20at%20Earth%20Tatva%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Earth%20Tatva%20in%20July%202023.%20My%20role%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20developing%20new%20compositions%20for%20recycled%20ceramic%20bodies%20and%20testing%20various%20glazes%20and%20colours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetteri